6. Deviation Bucket Summaries
	‚Ä¢	Groupwise Buckets: Automatically created using adjusted thresholds; highlights trades beyond max thresholds.
	‚Ä¢	Expanded Buckets: Fixed bin sizes for high-deviation trades; useful for analyzing outliers.
	‚Ä¢	Both summaries support:
	‚Ä¢	Dual-currency mapping
	‚Ä¢	Pivoting
	‚Ä¢	Filtering
	‚Ä¢	Download

